{"id":16,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":16,"title":"D&C 12","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 12"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to Joseph Knight Sr., at Harmony, Pennsylvania, May 1829. Joseph Knight believed the declarations of Joseph Smith concerning his possession of the Book of Mormon plates and the work of translation then in progress and several times had given material assistance to Joseph Smith and his scribe, which enabled them to continue translating. At Joseph Knight’s request, the Prophet inquired of the Lord and received the revelation."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.1-6"},"1–6"],", Laborers in the vineyard are to gain salvation;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.7-9"},"7–9"],", All who desire and are qualified may assist in the Lord’s work."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.1","order":"06.05.012.1807"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"A"],"great and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"marvelous work"],"is about to come forth among the children of men."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.2","order":"06.05.012.1808"},["b","2"],"Behold, I am God; give heed to my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"word"],", which is quick and powerful, sharper than a two-edged sword, to the dividing asunder of both joints and marrow; therefore, give heed unto my word."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.3","order":"06.05.012.1809"},["b","3"],"Behold, the field is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"white"],"already to harvest; therefore, whoso desireth to reap let him thrust in his sickle with his might, and reap while the day lasts, that he may treasure up for his soul everlasting salvation in the kingdom of God."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.4","order":"06.05.012.1810"},["b","4"],"Yea, whosoever will thrust in his sickle and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"reap"],", the same is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"called"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.5","order":"06.05.012.1811"},["b","5"],"Therefore, if you will ask of me you shall receive; if you will knock it shall be opened unto you."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.6","order":"06.05.012.1812"},["b","6"],"Now, as you have asked, behold, I say unto you, keep my commandments, and seek to bring forth and establish the cause of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.7","order":"06.05.012.1813"},["b","7"],"Behold, I speak unto you, and also to all those who have desires to bring forth and establish this work;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.8","order":"06.05.012.1814"},["b","8"],"And no one can assist in this work except he shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"humble"],"and full of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"love"],", having faith, hope, and charity, being temperate in all things, whatsoever shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"entrusted"],"to his care."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.9","order":"06.05.012.1815"},["b","9"],"Behold, I am the light and the life of the world, that speak these words, therefore give heed with your might, and then you are called. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.1a","order":"06.05.012.1816"},["b","1a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.1-6"},"D&C 11:1–6"],"for similar concepts and cross-references."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.1b","order":"06.05.012.1818"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14"},"Isa. 29:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/4.1.1-4"},"D&C 4:1 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.2a","order":"06.05.012.1820"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/4.12"},"Heb. 4:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.3a","order":"06.05.012.1822"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/4.4"},"D&C 4:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.3"},"14:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.3.3,7"},"33:3 (3, 7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.64"},"101:64"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.4a","order":"06.05.012.1824"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.15"},"Rev. 14:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.4b","order":"06.05.012.1826"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.4"},"D&C 6:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.4.3-4,27"},"11:4 (3–4, 27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.4.3-4"},"14:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.6a","order":"06.05.012.1828"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.8"},"Isa. 52:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.8a","order":"06.05.012.1830"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.8b","order":"06.05.012.1832"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/charity"},"TG Charity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"Faith"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"Hope"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"Love"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temperance"},"Temperance"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.8c","order":"06.05.012.1834"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4"},"1 Thes. 2:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.113"},"D&C 124:113"],"."]]}
